\frac{\sin3x}{\sin x}\cdot\frac{\sin(2n+1)x}{\sin x}=\frac{\sin(2n-1)x}{\sin x}+\frac{\sin(2n+1)x}{\sin x}+\frac{\sin(2n+3)x}{\sin x}
\sin C+\sin D=2\sin\frac{C+D}2\cos\frac{C-D}2,
\sin(2n-1)x+\sin(2n+3)x=2\sin(2n+1)x\cos 2x
\cos2x=1-2\sin^2x,
\frac{\sin(2n+1)x}{\sin x}
2\cos2x+1 =2(1-2\sin^2x)+1=3-4\sin^2x=\frac{3\sin x-4\sin^3x}{\sin^2x}=\frac{\sin3x}{\sin^2x}
